{"word":"Armies","slug":"armies","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Armies</b> Who of the Israelites were subject to service in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=3'>Num 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=2'>Num 26:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=5'>2Ch 25:5</a><br/> Who were exempt from service in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=50'>Num 1:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=33'>Num 2:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=5&chapter=20&verse=9'>Deu 20:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=3'>Jdg 7:3</a><br/> Enumeration of Israel's military forces<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=1&verse=3'>Num 1:3</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=26&verse=2'>Num 26:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=11&verse=8'>1Sa 11:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=2'>2Sa 18:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=24&verse=9'>2Sa 24:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=11&chapter=20&verse=15'>1Ki 20:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=5'>2Ch 25:5</a><br/> Levies for<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=4'>Num 31:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=20&verse=10'>Jdg 20:10</a><br/> Compulsory service in<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=52'>1Sa 14:52</a><br/><a href='S:Cowardice'>Cowardice</a><br/> How officered:<br/> - Commander-in-chief<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=14&verse=50'>1Sa 14:50</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=8'>2Sa 2:8</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=8&verse=16'>2Sa 8:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=17&verse=25'>2Sa 17:25</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=19&verse=13'>2Sa 19:13</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=23'>2Sa 20:23</a> <br/> - Generals of corps and divisions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2&verse=31'>Num 2:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=27&verse=22'>1Ch 27:22</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=17&verse=19'>2Ch 17:19</a> <br/> - Captains of thousands<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=14'>Num 31:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=48'>Num 31:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=18'>1Sa 17:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28&verse=1'>1Ch 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=5'>2Ch 25:5</a> <br/> - Captains of hundreds<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=14'>Num 31:14</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=31&verse=48'>Num 31:48</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=11&verse=15'>2Ki 11:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=28&verse=1'>1Ch 28:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=25&verse=5'>2Ch 25:5</a> <br/> - Captains of fifties<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=1&verse=9'>2Ki 1:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=3&verse=3'>Isa 3:3</a><br/><a href='S:Cavalry'>Cavalry</a>; <a href='S:Chariot'>Chariot</a> <br/> Rendezvous of<br/> - Methods employed in effecting:<br/> b Sounding a trumpet<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=10&verse=9'>Num 10:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=3&verse=27'>Jdg 3:27</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=6&verse=34'>Jdg 6:34</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=4'>1Sa 13:4</a><br/> b Cutting oxen in pieces, and sending the pieces throughout Israel<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=11&verse=7'>1Sa 11:7</a><br/> - Refusal to obey the summons, instance of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=21&verse=11'>Jdg 21:11</a>; <a href='B:'></a> <br/> Tactics:<br/> - Camp and march<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=4&chapter=2'>Num 2</a> <br/> - March in ranks<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=2&chapter=13&verse=18'>Exo 13:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=13&chapter=12&verse=33'>1Ch 12:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=29&chapter=2&verse=7'>Joe 2:7</a> <br/> - Move, in attack, in three divisions<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=7&verse=16'>Jdg 7:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=9&verse=43'>Jdg 9:43</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=11&verse=11'>1Sa 11:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=13&verse=18'>1Sa 13:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=2'>2Sa 18:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=18&chapter=1&verse=17'>Job 1:17</a> <br/> - Flanks called wings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=8&verse=8'>Isa 8:8</a><br/><a href='S:Strategy in War'>Strategy in War</a> <br/> Orders delivered with trumpets<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=2&verse=28'>2Sa 2:28</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=18&verse=16'>2Sa 18:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&verse=1'>2Sa 20:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=20&vers