apter=17&verse=14'>2Sa 17:14</a> <br/> - Celerity of action:<br/> b Abraham, in pursuit of Chedorlaomer<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=14&verse=15'>Gen 14:15</a><br/> b Joshua, against the Amorites<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=6'>Jos 10:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=10&verse=9'>Jos 10:9</a><br/> b the confederated kings<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=11&verse=7'>Jos 11:7</a><br/> b David's attack upon the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=25'>2Sa 5:25</a><br/> - Forced marches<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=23&chapter=5&verse=27'>Isa 5:27</a> <br/> - Sieges:<br/> b General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=39&verse=1'>Jer 39:1</a><br/> b of Jericho<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=6'>Jos 6</a><br/> b of Samaria<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=6&verse=33'>2Ki 6:33</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=7'>2Ki 7</a><br/> b of Jerusalem<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=3'>2Ki 25:3</a><br/> - &#187;Engines&#171; used<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=15'>2Ch 26:15</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=24&chapter=6&verse=6'>Jer 6:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=26&chapter=26&verse=9'>Eze 26:9</a> <br/> - Fortifications<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=9&verse=31'>Jdg 9:31</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=5&verse=9'>2Sa 5:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=12&chapter=25&verse=1'>2Ki 25:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=11'>2Ch 11:11</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=26&verse=9'>2Ch 26:9</a>;